{"id":271881,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-河南固始县维权人士周德才二审判决书/","date":"2012-12-31T07:31:02Z","modified":"2012-12-31T07:31:02Z","title":"维权网 | 河南固始县维权人士周德才二审判决书","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员蒋理报道）河南省固始县维权人士周德才，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>被控“涉嫌聚众扰乱社会秩序罪”刑事拘留，同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>被以聚众扰乱社会秩序罪判刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>年后，周德才当庭提起上诉，委托北京莫少平律师事务所律师马纲权代理。马律师为周德才二审作了无罪辩护，但法院没有采信，最后法院二审于今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日作出维持一审判决的决定，裁定书认定周德才多次煽动、策划、组织多人聚众扰乱社会秩序，致使政府工作、项目无法进行，因此驳回上诉，维持原判。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>固始县看守所在二审判决下来的当天晚上就在将周德才送往服刑的监狱。周德才妻子赶去欲送周德才一些御寒的衣服，但没有等到她送到，周德才就被押走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下面是周德才的二审判决书：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-LVL7T1KLeBg/UOEmSPvBI-I/AAAAAAAAX1E/DnsTrHfG0-A/s1600/%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%A1%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-LVL7T1KLeBg/UOEmSPvBI-I/AAAAAAAAX1E/DnsTrHfG0-A/s320/%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%A1%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A1.JPG\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vpV1bCZH990/UOEmT4ildGI/AAAAAAAAX1M/rHT0mA6azh0/s1600/%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%A1%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A2.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vpV1bCZH990/UOEmT4ildGI/AAAAAAAAX1M/rHT0mA6azh0/s320/%E4%BA%8C%E5%AE%A1%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A2.JPG\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nPcSj2jFX4I/UOEmWFw-89I